<h2>We've received your request 🎫</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>

<p>
    Thanks for reaching out to RentEase Support. Your ticket has been created
    successfully and our team is already on it. You can reply to this ticket
    anytime from your Support Center.
</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Ticket Summary</h3>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Ticket Number</th>
            <td><strong>{{ticketNumber}}</strong></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Subject</th>
            <td>{{subject}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Priority</th>
            <td>
                <span style="display:inline-block; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:12px; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; text-transform:capitalize;
                    {{#if (eq priority 'critical')}}background:#fee2e2; color:#7f1d1d;
                    {{else if (eq priority 'urgent')}}background:#fef2f2; color:#ef4444;
                    {{else if (eq priority 'high')}}background:#fef3c7; color:#b45309;
                    {{else if (eq priority 'low')}}background:#f1f5f9; color:#475569;
                    {{else}}background:#eff6ff; color:#2563eb;{{/if}}">
                    {{priority}}
                </span>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

<h3>Your Message</h3>
<p style="white-space: pre-wrap; color:#555;">{{description}}</p>

{{#if ticketUrl}}
<center>
    <a href="{{ticketUrl}}" class="button">View Your Ticket</a>
</center>
{{/if}}

<div class="info-box" style="border-left-color:#21a056;">
    <p style="margin:0;"><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
    <ul style="margin:10px 0 0 0; padding-left:20px;">
        <li>Our support team reviews your ticket and responds based on its priority.</li>
        <li>You'll get an email whenever there's an update.</li>
        <li>You can add more details or attachments by replying in the Support Center.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<p style="font-size: 13px; color:#888;">
    Please keep your ticket number <strong>{{ticketNumber}}</strong> handy for any
    future correspondence about this issue.
</p>

<p>We're here to help,<br>The RentEase Support Team</p>
